# IFDC Asset Management Platform — Phase 1 Implementation Plan

## Overview

Build the foundational architecture for a secure, scalable asset management system for the Ibn Firnas Drone Center. Phase 1 covers: project scaffolding, PostgreSQL relational schema, JWT authentication, and RBAC middleware.

**Tech Stack:** Go (Gin) · React (Vite + TypeScript + Tailwind CSS v4) · PostgreSQL · JWT

---

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> The existing `frontend/` was scaffolded with plain JavaScript. This plan **deletes and re-scaffolds** it with TypeScript + Tailwind CSS. If you want to keep the existing JS scaffold, let me know.

> [!IMPORTANT]
> The Go backend will use the **Gin** framework (most mature ecosystem, middleware-friendly, excellent community). If you prefer **Fiber** instead, let me know before I proceed.

---

